  "text": "The introduction of real estate tax would theoretically have a certain impact on the real estate prices, however, there are a large number of influencing factors to the prices and the relationship of them are very complex. So we need to quantify the impact of tax changes on prices. With the system dynamics software-Vensim PLE to establish the causal relationship of the influence factors, we use the historical data of 2001-2012 to operate the system simulation and model test, meanwhile forecast the impact on the future price [CITATION_1] .",
